WEBVTT

00:04:27.088 --> 00:04:30.363
inatokana na swali hili kubwa la msingi,

00:04:30.363 --> 00:04:32.033
nalo ni;

00:04:32.033 --> 00:04:34.341
Zingatia hali mbili.

00:04:34.341 --> 00:04:39.577
Hali A inaua asilimia 90 ya binadamu.

00:04:39.577 --> 00:04:43.473
Hali B inaua asilimia 100.

00:04:43.473 --> 00:04:46.391
Je B ni mbaya kiasi gani kuliko A?

00:04:46.391 --> 00:04:49.414
Baadhi watasema ni asilimia 10 mbaya
zaidi.

00:04:49.414 --> 00:04:52.564
Idadi ni asilimia 10 zaidi.

00:04:52.564 --> 00:04:55.470
Lakini nasema kua B ni mbaya zaidi.

00:04:55.470 --> 00:04:58.099
Kama mwanafalaki, siamini

00:04:58.099 --> 00:05:00.566
binadamu ni mwisho wa hadithi.